notes
We plan to observe vertical motion of polar cap patches with ESR.
We prefer good weather conditions during nights for possible 
comparison with the simultaneously operating optical instruments 
at KHO.

EROS commands:

pointdir 90 75
run /kst/exp/beata/beata fm patch NI
enablerec all



